data.value: SELECT [cspot2] , [pred] , [pretenzii] , [date_rassmoter] , [summa] , Convert(int, [oplacheno]) as oplacheno , [note] , [id_res] , [id_user_urist] , [date_pretenzii] , [prom_byt] FROM [urist].[dbo].[otchet_pretenzii] where (dateadd(day, -5, date_pretenzii) between @sdate and @podate) and (id_user_urist=@id_user_urist1 or id_user_urist=@id_user_urist2 or id_user_urist=@id_user_urist3 or id_user_urist=@id_user_urist4 or id_user_urist=@id_user_urist5 ) and prom_byt=2
